### LMS API Service Examples

### Create a Course
POST http://localhost:3001/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Introduction to TypeScript",
  "description": "Learn TypeScript fundamentals and best practices",
  "category": "Programming",
  "tags": ["typescript", "programming", "web", "javascript"]
}

### Get All Courses
GET http://localhost:3001/courses

### Get All Courses with User Completion
GET http://localhost:3001/courses?userId=user-123

### Get a Specific Course
GET http://localhost:3001/courses/{{courseId}}

### Get a Specific Course with Completion Percentage
GET http://localhost:3001/courses/{{courseId}}?userId=user-123

### Update a Course
PATCH http://localhost:3001/courses/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### Delete a Course
DELETE http://localhost:3001/courses/{{courseId}}

### Create a Lesson
POST http://localhost:3001/lessons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "TypeScript Basics",
  "content": "TypeScript is a typed superset of JavaScript that compiles to plain JavaScript. It adds optional types, classes, and modules to JavaScript.",
  "orderIndex": 1,
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}"
}

### Get All Lessons
GET http://localhost:3001/lessons

### Get Lessons by Course
GET http://localhost:3001/lessons?courseId={{courseId}}

### Get a Specific Lesson
GET http://localhost:3001/lessons/{{lessonId}}

### Update a Lesson
PATCH http://localhost:3001/lessons/{{lessonId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Lesson Title"
}

### Delete a Lesson
DELETE http://localhost:3001/lessons/{{lessonId}}

### Mark Lesson as Completed
POST http://localhost:3001/lessons/{{lessonId}}/complete?userId=user-123

### Get User Statistics
GET http://localhost:3001/users/user-123/stats

